<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>ilo devfile on ilo</title><link>https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/devfile/</link><description>Recent content in ilo devfile on ilo</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/devfile/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Options</title><link>https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/devfile/options/</link><pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/devfile/options/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;ilo devfile&lt;/code&gt; command can be configured with the following command line options. From your terminal, use &lt;code&gt;ilo devfile --help&lt;/code&gt; to get a list of all options, and their default values.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="--component"&gt;&lt;code&gt;--component&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;--component&lt;/code&gt; option can be used to tell &lt;code&gt;ilo&lt;/code&gt; which devfile component to use. At the moment only &lt;code&gt;container&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;image&lt;/code&gt; components are supported.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-console" data-lang="console"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="gp"&gt;#&lt;/span&gt; use specified component
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="gp"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt; ilo devfile --component some-name
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="err"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="gp"&gt;#&lt;/span&gt; auto-select component
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="gp"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt; ilo devfile
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;By default, &lt;code&gt;--component&lt;/code&gt; is not set, and &lt;code&gt;ilo&lt;/code&gt; uses the first component it can open.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>